  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "2. Add onion and sauté for 3-4 minutes until softened.",
    "3. Add ginger and sauté for an additional 1 minute.",
    "4. Add curry paste and sauté for 1-2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "5. Add dal broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "6. Add lentils and cook for 20-25 minutes until tender.",
    "7. Stir in sugar, fish sauce, and salt.",
    "8. Serve over fluffy jasmine rice.",
    "9. Garnish with fresh herbs if desired.",
    "10. Serve immediately."
